We're Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning.
Expert Service, Guaranteed. That's our commitment to you... and we put it in writing with our 100% Satisfaction Guarantee. Service Experts is your source for central air conditioning repairs and furnace repairs because we sell, service and install more air conditioning and heating systems than any other HVAC service company in North America.
If you need a job done right, you bring in the experts. At Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning in Niagara Falls, we’re passionate about performing quality HVAC services. We even put it in writing. Our 100% Satisfaction Guarantee displays our commitment to upholding the highest level of heating and air conditioning services in the industry. As a matter of fact, Service Experts in Niagara Falls repairs, sells and installs more heating and cooling systems than any other HVAC repair and service company in all of North America – more people entrust us with their home’s heating and cooling, so you can rest easy knowing your home is in good hands.

Service Experts in Niagara Falls will take care of all your home comfort needs. Whether your air conditioner or furnace breaks at the moment you need it most or you’re looking for indoor air quality solutions that meet the highest EPA and ENERGY STAR® standards, you can trust our Niagara Falls team. We’re experts in heating and air conditioning, and superior service is what we do best.

HEATING:
Furnace Repair Service, Furnace Sales, Furnace Installation, Furnaces & Air Handlers, Furnace Maintenance

COOLING:
AC Repair Service, New Air Conditioners, Air Conditioning Maintenance, Solar Air Conditioning, New Air Conditioners

COMMERCIAL:
If your work entails facility management, Peel Heating Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning in Brampton offers you the quality, dependability, and cost savings you want for your operations. No other company knows the HVAC industry like we do. With more than 90 heating and air conditioning service centers across North America, we offer an unparalleled level of skill and experience to service and provide solutions to your commercial heating and cooling needs. With NATE-trained technicians, high-tech energy solutions, 24/7/365 live customer service and more, we will exceed your expectations as experts in the HVAC industry.

INDOOR AIR QUALITY:
Not to be a killjoy, but are you inside? If so, you most likely be surprised if you realized how many toxins you may have just inhaled, including chemical vapors, microbes, mildew, viruses, bacteria, dust, dirt, pollen, allergens and more. Hold on...what?

The EPA discovered in a survey that Americans spend 87% of their lives inside, and that indoor air pollutant levels are up to 100 times higher than pollution levels found outside. Yikes! Now think about the fact that people breathe an estimated 3,000 gallons of air every single day. So do your kids. So does your Pug. Seriously, we need to stop taking indoor air quality for granted. Not anymore.

products:
Furnace Repair Service

Whether your unit stops working on your way to work or the middle of the night, we can be out to service your furnace in no time. Our NATE-certified technicians have received the most prestigious training and certification in the industry, so they’ll do the job right the first time. Our expert professionals at Service Experts in Niagara Falls are trained to service any kind of furnace or boiler, so you can be sure you’ll get the best service out there.
Furnace Sales & Installation

Purchasing a new furnace is a big deal. Do you know where to begin? Don’t worry. Our expert heating and cooling consultants will help you decide which unit is best for your specific home based on the size of your home, your family’s air quality needs, financing budget and your desired energy efficiency. One of our experts will work with you every step of the way from choosing the best system and financing solution, to carrying out an expert equipment installation when it arrives.
Furnaces & Air Handlers

If you’re in the market for a new furnace or air handler, look no further than Service Experts in Niagara Falls. We sell a wide selection of gas furnaces, oil furnaces, air handlers, boilers and garage heaters – and all our products feature energy efficiency, low noise levels and, of course, durable performance. Check out our full range of products on the Furnaces & Air Handlers page.
Furnace Maintenance

You can’t completely prevent your furnace from breaking down, but you can help thwart it with annual furnace maintenance visits. Our in-depth furnace tune-ups and PLUS service plans actually help you save in two ways. First, a well-maintained unit will run more efficiently and uses less energy, which is good for the environment. Second, proper maintenance means fewer expensive repairs. We don’t know about you, but we have a list of things we’d rather spend money for. And with lower energy bills, we can!

AC repair doesn't have to be a pain. Sure, you’re probably not in your happiest moment when you need us, but rest assured, we’re standing by to take care of any AC repair issue that arrives. We’re certified to service all brands of air conditioners, so you know you’ll be getting the best AC repair available. And with a written 100% Satisfaction Guarantee you have nothing to lose.

New Air Conditioners:
The time has come to finally take the next step to updating your home’s air conditioner. Upgrading your current system is actually more affordable than you may think, so why wait any longer? Scheduling a FREE estimate is easy too. Just fill in your information and we’ll work with you to make your home cool, energy efficient, and the most comfortable it has ever been.

Air Conditioning Maintenance:
So you’ve got your thermostat programmed perfectly but you’re still not satisfied with your energy bill every month? Much like cars, AC maintenance is vital to ensure your home is running at its top efficiency. We’ve created four service plans to meet your exact AC maintenance need, as well as your budget.

Solar Air Conditioning:
We won’t inundate you with a bunch of “green” terminology, but you should know that solar air conditioning is a lot more affordable and practical than you make think. We have countless products that can take your home to the next level of efficiency and also provide your wallet with a little more green as well. While you shouldn’t stare into the sun, you should definitely take a look into utilizing all the power it provides.

Air Conditioners:
We all like being comfortable. Keeping your home cool plays a big part in your family’s comfort in the heat of the summer and we’re here to help ensure you maintain the level of comfort your need. Choosing one of our ENERGY STAR® qualified air conditioners will keep your home the most comfortable temperature while giving you a quiet and efficient system that helps lessen your carbon footprint at the same time.
